---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = 'The Gemini App is now available on Mac OS';
const description = 'Google 将 Gemini 应用带到 macOS，提供原生桌面体验。';
---

<Layout 
  title={title}
  description={description}
  type="article"
  publishedTime="2026-04-16"
  tags={["AI-Agents", "Agent-Economy", "Future-of-Work"]}
>
  <article class="article-content">
    <h1 class="lang-content lang-zh active">Gemini 应用现已登陆 Mac OS</h1>
    <h1 class="lang-content lang-en">The Gemini App is now available on Mac OS</h1>
    
    <time datetime="2026-04-16">2026-04-16</time>
    
    <div class="lang-content lang-zh active">
      <p>Google 将 Gemini 应用带到 macOS，提供原生桌面体验。</p>
      <p><a href="https://blog.google/innovation-and-ai/products/gemini-app/gemini-app-now-on-mac-os/" target="_blank">阅读原文</a></p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="lang-content lang-en">
      <p>Google is bringing the Gemini app to macOS as a native desktop experience.</p>
      <p><a href="https://blog.google/innovation-and-ai/products/gemini-app/gemini-app-now-on-mac-os/" target="_blank">Read the full article</a></p>
    </div>
    
    <a href="/" class="back-link">← Back to articles</a>
  </article>
</Layout>
